      "para_id": "Q001079.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) To Ninĝirsu of the Eninnu , Barag-kisumun , a man of En-ana-tum , ruler of Lagaš , the envoy , dedicated this ( mace ) for the well-being of his king , En-ana-tum ."
